{"tid":1304300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請大家focus翻個焦點。","createTime":"2019-07-10T14:39:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T01:35:59.000Z","uid":266601,"like":61,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"c1247057591e2166acf0170e7d135a685e390182","tid":1304300,"uid":266601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:39:31.000Z","msg":"重視個連儂牆唔緊要<br />\n但係我地已經有5個烈士，有67名義士被捕<br />\n真係唔好再focus喺牆同埋廣告住<br />\n我知打飛機好重要<br />\n但係咪打咁多，對個運動冇利，正苦都唔會理9你。<br />\n<br />\n記得！<br />\n<br />\n重申抗爭所堅持之五大訴求:<br />\n一、撤回修例<br />\n二、撤回6.12暴動定性<br />\n三、撤銷反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、責成獨立調查委員會追究警方濫權<br />\n五、實行雙真普選<br />\n<br />\n快啲討論死線，然後升級，和理非又好勇武又好都要升級<br />\n文宣嘅文宣，發夢嘅發夢<br />\n咁先做到兄弟爬山，各自修行以及遍地開花之作用！<br />\n<br />\n巴絲們，我地為自由而繼續加油！<br />\n運動尚未成功，同志們仍需努力，加油！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hvr7DfE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhvr7DfE.png&h=9dc35c09&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"10dab6be793099edae40848178406078b58d2b57","tid":1304300,"uid":266601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:42:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1afd0ace4b3a59e92d24815eda52cf059c9a80c3","tid":1304300,"uid":266601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:42:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faa786e7a9633689adb47dea2401c990daed5379","tid":1304300,"uid":266601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:44:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"579191be75bda8fd6dd0a8707aac26a0e9631bc8","tid":1304300,"uid":34478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:45:15.000Z","msg":"<img sr